(15284, 'Biomox 1 gm vial', 'بيوموكس 1 جرام فيال', '', '14', 'Amoxicillin', 'Sedico', 'Vial', 'فيال', '', 'Penicillins.monocomponent', '1 gm', 'Amoxicillin alone is indicated to treat susceptible bacterial infections of the ear, nose, throat, genitourinary tract, skin, skin structure, and lower respiratory tract.[L11656,L11659] Amoxicillin is given with calvulanic acid to treat acute bacterial sinusitis, community acquired pneumonia, lower respiratory tract infections, acute bacterial otitis media, skin and skin structure infections, and urinary tract infections.[L11650,L7880,L11653] Amoxicillin is given with omeprazole in the treatment of _Helicobacter pylori_ (_H. pylori_) infection.[L9743,L11647]
